title: Lester Bowie's Brass Fantasy - My Way (1990) [EAC-FLAC]
description:
1. Quasi (Bruce Purse, arr. by E. J. Allen)
2. Who Says (Bruce Purse, arr. by Steve Turre)
3. After Thought (Bruce Purse, arr. by E. J. Allen)
